<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>34</hymn_number>
<author>Ralngam</author>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. A guotuh Lal Immanuel,
 Adam suon gitloh ziekin;
 Van sana khawpi tuolnuom nusie'n,
 Judai gam Bethlehem ah;
 Mun a um puoi Lal pien na'n,
 Bethlehem ah gankuong sung A ngak.

[V2]
 Lawpin chawian hitiu,
 I Tanpau A pieng tai;
 Hallelujah A min pakchai tiu,
 Lei chungah cham leng hen,
 Nam zetin te a di'n,
 Ei uh din damna A hun tun hi.

[V3]
 2. Kaisar lal min ziklai khan
 Judai gam Belampute;
 A kimuh Lal lopi'n A salhvak,
 &quot;Lau kiu inla, ngaitiem u;
 Thu kipahum ka hun tun,
 Hukdampa A hung pieng tai&quot; a tii.

[V4]
 3. &quot;Ngailo Na him Hukdampa,
 Na van khawpi tuol nuom chu;
 Bang die gan kuong sunga kuol na him?
 &quot;Aw ka ngai ka van khawpi,
 Mahleh nang gitloh ziekin,
 Lei dahum thim ah albang Ka vai&quot;

[V5]
 4. Khawvel lal tamtak a pieng,
 In hawih lopitak sungah;
 En tie, van lal pienna bawng In khu,
 Ka thagau, na Lal a hi,
 Chieh in hawl in gan kuong ah
 A chunnu liengthei Mari'n a pawm.</lyrics>
<title>Lal Immanuel</title>
</song>